{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1013984, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202146, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "认为政治课是洗脑，本身是不是洗脑？", "timestamp": 1611917513, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014027, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 202146, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "没问题啊？", "timestamp": 1611917689, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014031, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 202146, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "哪个国家政治课不是洗脑？", "timestamp": 1611917703, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014046, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202146, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 因为书里直接说明你需要怎么做，怎么做一定是对的，不允许异见", "timestamp": 1611917773, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014056, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202146, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 可以举一些tw、hk等地的例子吗？是不是意味着它们这样做也没问题", "timestamp": 1611917843, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014072, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 202146, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "难道不就是洗脑吗？\n反正政治课的事实我会听，应该怎么做我就把它转化成领导人的观点。。", "timestamp": 1611917968, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014086, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202146, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 只是抖个机灵啦。严格来说，政治课书本其实就是应试教育，有标准答案的情况下当然要遵循书本的规则，政治课和政治思想教育本身无关。", "timestamp": 1611918052, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014134, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 202146, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 想请教一下政治思想教育为什么和政治课无关？那是怎么培养的", "timestamp": 1611918275, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014138, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 202146, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "俺还以为是把学生洗得厌恶马克思主义呢", "timestamp": 1611918295, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014281, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 202146, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: Alice的意思是这更多算是一个面对政治课的态度吧。顶层设计时认为政治课是思想政治教育，但是实际上现在的政治课很难起到思想政治教育的作用，特别是和应试结合的情况下（比如我们背诵的全盘接受苏联教科书体系的很多时候不容置疑的东西，基本会引起学习者的逆反）。\nAlice觉得，基于灌输论的当前政治课模式可能是难以为继的，具体的思想政治教育，应当从实践和现实入手。", "timestamp": 1611919259, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1014601, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 202146, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "那政治课设计的挺失败的，基本起了反作用", "timestamp": 1611923546, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 4, "pid": 202146, "reply": 11, "tag": "政治相关", "text": "#政治相关\n当有人说学政治课是洗脑时该如何反驳？（政治书中的标准答案，坚持听从..领导）", "timestamp": 1611917396, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1611923546, "url": "", "vote": {}}}